# Decentralized Insurance Protocol

A comprehensive blockchain-based insurance system built on the Stacks blockchain that enables transparent, trustless insurance operations through smart contracts.

##  Features

- **Dynamic Policy Creation**: Create customizable insurance policies with flexible coverage limits and premium structures
- **Automated Premium Collection**: Seamless premium payment processing with detailed transaction tracking
- **Transparent Claims Processing**: Open and verifiable claims submission and adjudication workflow
- **Decentralized Management**: Policy holders maintain full control over their insurance policies
- **Real-time Balance Management**: Live tracking of contract funds and financial status
- **Immutable Records**: All insurance transactions are permanently recorded on the blockchain
- **Emergency Controls**: Secure administrative functions for emergency fund management

